widgets_values: The parts enabled in the LayerMask node are the parts that will go through an additional detailing pass (perfect for adding stretch marks, blemishes and skin imperfection)

If you're getting memory errors, right click the Ultimate SD Upscale node > Convert Input to Widget > change both tile_width and tile_height to widget > set to a size that works for you (512,768,1024)
Write your prompts and pick your desired resolution
